## Setup

```bash
# 1. Install Python dependencies
pip install pytest pytest-playwright

# 2. Install Playwright browser (Chromium only required)
playwright install chromium

# 3. Copy conftest template (if not already done)
cp <lean-kit>/modules/testing-e2e/templates/conftest.py.template tests/e2e/conftest.py

# 4. Open conftest.py and replace every {{PLACEHOLDER}} with spoke-specific values
