## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all E2E tests
pytest tests/e2e/

# Run with HTML report (required for AOS QA evidence attachment)
pytest tests/e2e/ --html=tests/e2e/report.html --self-contained-html

# Run a single test file
pytest tests/e2e/test_<feature>.py

# Run with Playwright trace (attach as evidence zip for complex failures)
pytest tests/e2e/ --tracing=on
```

