## Writing Tests

Use `auth_page` for any test that requires a logged-in user:

```python
def test_dashboard_loads(auth_page):
    auth_page.goto("/dashboard")
    assert auth_page.title() == "Dashboard"
```

Use a plain `page` fixture (from pytest-playwright) for unauthenticated flows:

```python
def test_login_page_renders(page):
    page.goto("/login")
    assert page.locator("h1").text_content() == "Sign In"
```

