## AOS Evidence Conventions

When E2E tests are required by Team 50 in a QA_REQUEST, attach evidence as:

| Evidence type | How to generate | Attach as |
|---------------|----------------|-----------|
| HTML report | `pytest --html=report.html` | `evidence_e2e_report` in QA_REQUEST |
| Playwright trace | `pytest --tracing=on` → `test-results/*/trace.zip` | `evidence_e2e_trace` in QA_REQUEST |

See `_aos/lean-kit/modules/testing-e2e/docs/TEAM_50_E2E_STANDARD_v1.0.0.md` for the
full decision matrix on when E2E evidence is required vs. optional.

